look thru the gallery for the rest, 5 total.

This bus has a new rebuilt engine, good trans, new tires and brakes, she was
on her maiden voyage when this happened. The trans is locked up and I don't
know the condition of the engine, hopefully it was shut off and not run till
it stopped when the bus was on it's side. The tires have rocks in the beads
but still hold air. About everything else on the bus in junk. Will have more
info on the outcome of the parts in a few days.

ronnie   aka volksrescue.com
www.type2parts.com



